Who’s on their “scram!” list for Take a Hike Day? Why is Tyler particularly fond of November 18th? Mark your calendars as they polish their Pig Latin for Absurdity Day, and discover why the Illuminati commemorates Looking for Circles Day.

episodes.seriesTitle: Psychobabble with Tyler Oakley & Korey Kuhl
episodes.title: PB 10: Taylor Swift - Queens Edition
episodes.summary: Show off your Swiftie pride! To honor the release of 1989, Tyler and Korey are dedicating this week’s conversation to Taylor Swift, the new queen of pop. Which of her albums are their favorite? What are 1989’s hottest tracks? Tune in as they share stories about meeting Taylor, swoon over her ex’s ass-abs, and Tyler performs his own rendition of “Our Song.”

episodes.seriesTitle: Psychobabble with Tyler Oakley & Korey Kuhl
episodes.title: PB 9: Halloween
episodes.summary: Throw on your spookiest costume for this week’s Halloween episode! It’s Christmas for the gays, but Tyler and Korey still have some details to figure out. Which trick-or-treat outfit should they wear? Why is Queen Jackie celebrating her new birthday on this holiday? Brace yourselves for some creepy conversations about their biggest fears, Ouija boards, and the most frightening sound of all...the gay gremlin witch cackle.

episodes.seriesTitle: Psychobabble with Tyler Oakley & Korey Kuhl
episodes.title: PB 8: Celebrity Drama
episodes.summary: Catch up on this week’s celebrity scandals. Why is Tyler so jealous of Ariana Grande? How did Snoop Dogg ruin National Bullying Prevention Month? Is Harry Styles the real inspiration behind Taylor Swift’s 1989? Dig up some dirt as Tyler and Korey also reveal whose topless photoshoot caused an Exorcist reaction, what happened on Tyler’s movie talker date, and why they’re actually interested in the Super Bowl this year.

episodes.seriesTitle: Psychobabble with Tyler Oakley & Korey Kuhl
episodes.title: PB 7: Celeb Conspiracy Theories
episodes.summary: Rumor vs. trumor - you be the judge. This week, Tyler and Korey debate about the latest celebrity conspiracy theories. Whose “hoo-hah” gave birth to the Antichrist? Which celebs are members of the Illuminati? Help the boys answer these wild speculations on Larry Stylinson, Beyonce’s real family tree, and Ke$ha’s pee-drinking habits.

episodes.seriesTitle: Psychobabble with Tyler Oakley & Korey Kuhl
episodes.title: PB 6: Coming Out Day
episodes.summary: Celebrate National Coming Out Day! In honor of this holiday, Tyler and Korey retrace their journey into the LGBT community. How did they first come out? Who are their favorite gay celebs? Join the festivities as these queens plan their own coming out parties, measure how gay Tyler really is, and share their best coming out tips.

episodes.seriesTitle: Psychobabble with Tyler Oakley & Korey Kuhl
episodes.title: PB 5: Slumber Parties
episodes.summary: Stay up late to this week’s pillow talk. In preparation for the Slumber Party tour, Tyler and Korey compare sleepover memories of pranking, pooping, and putting on a performance. But the boys aren’t done with pajama parties yet! Find out which celebs they want at future sleepovers and how you can bring Tyler’s Slumber Party to your city.

episodes.seriesTitle: Psychobabble with Tyler Oakley & Korey Kuhl
episodes.title: PB 4: Celebrity Gossip
episodes.summary: Get the scoop on Tyler and Korey’s favorite celebrity drama. Is Taylor vs. Katy just a rumor? Which band’s new album is worse than herpes? Don’t miss this week’s gossip on pop queen conspiracies, the best organ to swap for an iPhone, and the mystery about teeth and bones.

episodes.seriesTitle: Psychobabble with Tyler Oakley & Korey Kuhl
episodes.title: PB 3: Troye Sivan
episodes.summary: Meet Troye Sivan, YouTube star and pop’s newest sensation. On this week’s episode, he joins Tyler and Korey to discuss some very pressing matters. What is “Happy Little Pill” really about? Which country has the best kissers? And why is he so fascinated with Korey’s big vein?

episodes.seriesTitle: Psychobabble with Tyler Oakley & Korey Kuhl
episodes.title: PB 2: High School
episodes.summary: Learn how Tyler and Korey survived high school. This week, they reminisce on crying teachers, reveal the truth about test scores, and investigate where exactly Tyler got his cheerleading skills (Hint: there’s a visit from Queen Jackie).

episodes.seriesTitle: Psychobabble with Tyler Oakley & Korey Kuhl
episodes.title: PB 1: The Bestie
episodes.summary: Find out how Tyler and Korey became besties. Where did they meet? Who crushed on who? In this first episode, they also tell tales of flirting in the drive thru, stumbling into the world of YouTube, and becoming crack buddies with Tyler Posey.
